  "body": "Originally opened [at remix](https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/issues/2325)\r\nThen [at MetaMask](https://github.com/MetaMask/metamask-extension/issues/2999#issuecomment-397395577)\r\nThen [here at Geth](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/issues/14989) (but I think mis-represented, so prematurely closed).\r\n\r\nSolidity:\r\n```\r\npragma solidity ^0.4.11;\r\n\r\ncontract Test {\r\n  function balanceOfEther(address user) public constant returns (uint256) { return user.balance; } \r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nReturns unusual balances when requested from Geth via an eth_call.\r\n\r\nFor any address, returns:\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":570283474,\"result\":\"0xfffffffffffffffffffffffffffffffffffffffffffffffffdeb17cb73b0ffff\"}\r\n```",
